00:49:26,910 --> 00:49:30,903
Hey.

820
00:49:48,932 --> 00:49:52,925
§ I was dreaming §

821
00:49:53,737 --> 00:49:57,730
§ Of the past §

822
00:50:00,344 --> 00:50:03,580
§ And my heart §

823
00:50:03,580 --> 00:50:07,573
