1033
01:02:23,820 --> 01:02:26,156
and he says,

1034
01:02:26,156 --> 01:02:29,259
"Hey..."

1035
01:02:29,259 --> 01:02:31,061
No. He said,

1036
01:02:31,061 --> 01:02:34,030
